title._content: Gertrude Leffert Vanderbilt House, Lincoln Road and Flatbush Avenue, Brooklyn (near Brighton El), 1907.

description._content: Daniel Berry Austin (American, born 1863, active 1899-1909). Gertrude Leffert Vanderbilt House, Lincoln Road and Flatbush Avenue, Brooklyn (near Brighton El), 1907.
